headline: Fifth Third Becomes First Bank to Offer Free Wills to All Customers
summary: CINCINNATI, May 19, 2025--Fifth Third (NASDAQ: FITB) today announced a first-of-its-kind initiative to offer free wills to every customer, through an exclusive partnership with Trust & Will, the leading digital estate planning platform in the U.S.

headline: Fifth Third gives customers free access to wills
summary: The move reflects the bank’s aims to bolster its benefits for customers and do more with its fintech partners to differentiate itself from competitors, a Fifth Third VP said.
